Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.61,0:00:07.41,Lyrics2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,百 鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,頑固的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還不肯聽我的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說的話…絕對…不會聽的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.16,0:01:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來妳受的懲罰還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼我就好好的修理妳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧，含住吧，含住它讓我舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰會含這種髒東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫妳含住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽我的話！聽我的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳若堅持反抗，我就用硬來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常好，非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再來，再舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好，要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一滴不剩的喝乾它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰叫妳用咬的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是甚麼眼神？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小光，妳是我的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乖乖服從我，成為我忠實的女奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要，我死也不當你的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我就把妳裝飾起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把妳變成冰凍的肉人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣妳就是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把妳永遠擺在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰來…救救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我從當這個男人的人偶…解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:02:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰來…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:05.42,Lyrics1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三鬼  [若葉]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是誰幹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,篠原先生身上也有的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了？龍一君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,惠美小姐，是妳殺死他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍…龍一君，你在說甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳手上的繃帶下，是燒傷的痕跡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是為了掩飾…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,智子小姐，大石先生，以及篠原先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三人屍體上發現的燒傷的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是電擊槍的電流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以惠美小姐，妳繃帶下的傷痕也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你很清楚呢，龍一君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,惠美小姐，妳為何這麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的使命是排除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「他」所不滿意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡，竟然殺死智子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉政大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:04:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉政？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是我的主人，王光寺吉政大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫王光寺的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難…難道是這座大賀島的主人\N王光寺財團的總裁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,礙事者都消失掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍一先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家趕快逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之趕快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,高志先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別管我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉，趁現在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祥子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別做無意義的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉，快逃，快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只得若葉也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣就能照預定的得到新的奴隸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡被他們發現的疏忽\N我就姑且原諒妳了，惠美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你，吉政大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祥子，這…這麼激烈的話，我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對…對不起，宏美，可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祥…祥子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…宏美…我…宏美…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰准許妳們高潮的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉政大人的命令是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了，來讓我滿足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰會這麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反抗吉政大人是不可饒恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還想被懲罰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳們終於瞭解自己的立場了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給妳們獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰准許妳們停下來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個旅行企劃就是為了找新奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而被選上的人是妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要感到光榮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,逃走的另一個女人之後也會加入妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧\N請把吉政大人的牛奶一滴不剩的舔乾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別過來，若葉，快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉，快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,惠美，妳在幹甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過來這裡幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是，吉政大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祥子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不需擔心妳的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來輪到妳了，乖乖等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好哦，妳的狀況很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來我會好好的疼愛妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到了嗎？小光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本來應該是妳為我服務的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉政大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉，高志，快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉政大人，你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個沒用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉政大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可饒恕，我要殺死所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉政大人，你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉政大人，為甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對我沒用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反抗我的人全部該殺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來要怎麼辦？龍一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之趕快想辦法逃離島上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是，龍一先生\N無線電壞了，沒辦法找船來接人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定有辦法的，再想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了嗎？若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得帶小隆一起離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種時候不用管蘆薈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以不跟小隆一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉，不要再任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我無論再溫柔也是會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行，我要帶它走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人在哪裡？滾出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,高志\N宏美與祥子兩人就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起，小隆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只能帶走這一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要走了哦，若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有綠色的小島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直夢想著\N看到這座小島有綠色的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,滿是綠色的這座小島嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,高志他們到哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早知道就先決定會合地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起來\N集齊的話就可以達成心願的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只差一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在不是說那個的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於被我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傷害我的這個重罪，要你拿命來補償
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慢著，只是若葉，別對她下手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少囉嗦，不准求饒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要殺死所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大…大哥哥，你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傻瓜，妳幹甚麼這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥沒事的話…就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別再說了，若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很久以前，大哥哥也這樣抱過我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我以前也抱過被槍擊中的若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…要保護大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絕對…絕對…要保護…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉，振作起來啊，若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我送你們一起上天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道你是…八年前…那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那時候，我殺死了他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉政大人，惠美要一輩子服侍你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以…吉政大人…\N跟惠美…跟惠美一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吉政…大…人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:30.62,Lyrics1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,[八年前]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久沒來大賀島了，豐哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯，說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從這裡看過去的景色也沒有改變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小隆也很懷念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從小島疏散之後兩年了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照理來說，應該長很多雜草的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這座島果然由於海水的關係\N變得植物無法生長了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了\N把這十五個故事放在神社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了\N若葉，妳想許甚麼願望呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過，一定會讓大哥哥吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,提示是：小隆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於到這一刻了，大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救命啊，豐君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小光，這不是小光嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:17:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫小光小姐？\N跟大哥哥感情很好的三橋光小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小光，妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是我的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們別多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道秘密的人是非死不可了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉，妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,振作起來，若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥，我好像不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把不是親妹妹，只要青梅竹馬的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,疼愛到現在，謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳在胡說甚麼？我一定會救妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以妳要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從很久以前就有話要跟大哥哥說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甚麼？若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳有甚麼要說我都會聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喜歡大哥哥，一直喜歡著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以一個女人的身份，對大哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深愛著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你若把我當成女人，就吻我\N大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是我最後的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道我秘密的人都得從世界上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快逃，快逃啊，大哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了，全部想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是豐先生的重生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個夢，那個記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我對大賀島的一切都覺得熟悉\N就是這個緣故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好想見你啊，大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直等著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想再次…再次…見到大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥，那裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥，大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉，我們合為一體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧，大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣我與大哥哥是一體了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好高興，好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是，若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行\N大哥哥，大哥哥，大哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥，謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣我的回憶就沒有遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥，我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:22:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉，雖然終於…終於重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還是沒能救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最後的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事到如今，事到如今這東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言靈神社
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果真的獻上十五個故事\N就能達成願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的願望是…我的願望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:56.28,Lyrics0,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三鬼  [若葉] 完\N~後面還有後記~
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.98,0:25:29.68,Lyrics1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,[一個月後]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.58,0:26:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是…那些街道…？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.38,0:26:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉的願望實現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.18,0:26:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.08,0:26:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥，終於重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.08,0:26:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若葉，怎麼這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.08,0:26:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難…難道…？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.38,0:26:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言靈神社達成了大哥哥的願望
